        <h1>Reading books</h1>
        One of my favorite hobbies is reading books. I love getting lost in different worlds, meeting interesting characters, and exploring new ideas through stories. Whether it's a thrilling mystery, a heartwarming novel, or an informative nonfiction book, reading always keeps me engaged and entertained. It helps me relax, improves my vocabulary, and expands my knowledge about various topics. I enjoy spending quiet afternoons with a good book, completely immersed in its pages. Reading is not just a hobby for me; it’s a way to learn, imagine, and escape into a world of endless possibilities.</p>
