        <h1>Listening to music</h1>
        Another hobby of me which I do the most nowadays is listening to music. Music has a way of lifting my mood, helping me relax, and making every moment more enjoyable. Whether I’m feeling happy, sad, or stressed, there’s always a song that matches my emotions perfectly. I love exploring different genres, from pop and rock to classical and lo-fi, depending on my mood. Listening to music also helps me focus while studying or unwind after a long day. It’s more than just a hobby for me—it’s a way to express myself, find comfort, and escape into a world of melodies and lyrics.
